---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pagination:
  data: cityCountryComparisons
  size: 1
  alias: comp
permalink: "/compare/city-vs-country/{{ comp.slug }}/"
eleventyComputed:
  pageTitle: "{{ comp.city.name }} vs. {{ comp.country.name }}: 2026 Digital Nomad Comparison"
  pageDescription: "{{ comp.description }}"
---

<div class="section-container mt-16">
    {# Hero #}
    <div class="comparison-hero text-center mb-16">
        <div class="badge-2026 mb-4">
            <span style="display:inline-block; width:8px; height:8px; background:#10b981; border-radius:50%; margin-right:5px;"></span>
            2026 Strategic Relocation Analysis
        </div>
        <h1 class="aura-title">{{ comp.city.name }} vs. {{ comp.country.name }}<br>Lifestyle vs. Visa Comparison</h1>
        <p class="text-dim" style="font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 1rem auto 0;">⚖️ {{ comp.description }}</p>
    </div>

    {# Side-by-Side Cards #}
    <div class="comparison-grid">
        {# City Card #}
        <div class="comp-card" style="border-top: 6px solid var(--aura-primary);">
            <div class="flex-between mb-6">
                <h3 style="margin: 0;">{{ comp.city.name }}, {{ comp.city.country }}</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Type:</span> <strong>Specific City Base</strong></div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Monthly COL:</span> <strong>${{ comp.city.col | localeString }}</strong></div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Average Rent:</span> <strong>${{ comp.city.rent | localeString }}/mo</strong></div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Local Tax Rate:</span> <strong>{{ comp.city.tax | percentInt }}</strong></div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Nomad Score:</span> <strong>{{ comp.city.score }}/100</strong></div>
            
            <div class="verdict-box" style="background: rgba(var(--aura-primary-rgb), 0.05);">
                <p><strong>Ideal for: {{ comp.city.intro | truncate(60) }}</strong></p>
            </div>

            <h4 class="mt-8 mb-2">Top Reason to Choose {{ comp.city.name }}</h4>
            <p class="text-dim" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Living in {{ comp.city.name }} provides a verified nomad community, specific neighborhood vibes, and immediate access to {{ comp.city.name }}'s unique infrastructure.</p>
        </div>

        {# Country Card #}
        <div class="comp-card" style="border-top: 6px solid var(--aura-secondary);">
            <div class="flex-between mb-6">
                <h3 style="margin: 0;">{{ comp.country.name }} (Full Country)</h3>
                <span style="font-size: 2rem;">{{ comp.country.code | countryEmoji }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Type:</span> <strong>National Visa Program</strong></div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Visa Name:</span> <strong>{{ comp.country.visaName }}</strong></div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>National Tax:</span> <strong>{{ comp.country.tax | percentInt }}</strong></div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Min. Income:</span> <strong>${{ comp.country.minIncomeMonthly | localeString }}/mo</strong></div>
            <div class="stat-row"><span>Visa Length:</span> <strong>{{ comp.country.visaDuration }}</strong></div>

            <div class="verdict-box" style="background: rgba(var(--aura-secondary-rgb), 0.05);">
                <p><strong>Focus: National Residency & Tax</strong></p>
            </div>

            <h4 class="mt-8 mb-2">Benefits of {{ comp.country.name }}</h4>
            <ul class="text-dim" style="font-size: 0.9rem; padding-left: 1.2rem;">
                {% for highlight in comp.country.highlights %}
                <li>{{ highlight }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# Expert Analysis #}
    <div class="expert-analysis mt-16">
        <h2 class="mb-8">Expert Verdict: Choosing Between a City Base or a Country Strategy</h2>
        <p>Choosing <strong>{{ comp.city.name }}</strong> means committing to a specific urban lifestyle with known costs of ${{ comp.city.col | localeString }}/month. This is best for nomads who value community and established coworking hubs.</p>
        <p class="mt-6">However, <strong>{{ comp.country.name }}</strong>'s {{ comp.country.visaName }} might offer better long-term tax residency benefits ({{ comp.country.tax | percentInt }} flat rate) and the flexibility to move between multiple cities like {% for c in comp.country.cities %}{{ c }}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}.</p>
        
        <div class="glass-panel mt-8" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--aura-accent);">
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Relocation Tip:</strong> If you love the vibe of {{ comp.city.name }} but need the legal stability of {{ comp.country.name }}, check if there is a tax treaty between {{ comp.city.country }} and {{ comp.country.name }} before making your final move.</p>
        </div>

        {# Nomad Verdict #}
        <div class="glass-panel mt-8" style="border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05);">
            <div class="expert-verdict-content" style="display: flex; gap: 1.5rem;">
                <div class="expert-icon" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">🏗️</div>
                <div>
                    <h3 style="color: #f59e0b;" class="mb-4">2026 Hybrid Strategy</h3>
                    <p style="font-style: italic;" class="text-dim">"The smartest move for 2026? Use the <strong>{{ comp.country.name }} {{ comp.country.visaName }}</strong> to secure legal residency, but set up your primary base in <strong>{{ comp.city.name }}</strong>. This gives you the high-intensity networking of the city with the national-level tax benefits of the visa program."</p>
                    <div class="mt-6 stack-on-mobile" style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <div class="badge-2026" style="background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1); border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);">🏛️ National Protection</div>
                        <div class="badge-2026" style="background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1); border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);">☕ City Infrastructure</div>
                        <div class="badge-2026" style="background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1); border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);">🌍 Global Portability</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {# Relocation Toolkit #}
        <div class="mt-16">
            {% include "partials/relocation-toolkit.njk" %}
        </div>
    </div>

    {# Lead Magnet #}
    {% include "partials/lead-magnet.njk" %}

    {# Related Comparisons #}
    <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-8">Explore More Options</h2>
        <div class="partner-grid">
            {% for related in cityCountryComparisons | slice(0, 13) %}
            {% if related.slug != comp.slug %}
            <a href="/compare/city-vs-country/{{ related.slug }}/" class="partner-card">
                <h4>{{ related.city.name }} vs. {{ related.country.name }}</h4>
                <p>Strategic Comparison</p>
            </a>
            {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
